# Little Lemon Food Ordering App
This project is a food ordering app for the Little Lemon restaurant. It allows users to browse the menu, place orders, and manage their food selections.
## Features
- User-friendly interface
- Menu browsing
- Order placement
- User authentication
## Technologies Used
- Kotlin
- Android Studio
- Git for version control
## Installation
To run this project, clone the repository and open it in Android Studio.
